				\begin{document}$$R_{S}$$\end{document} where its satisfactory value is 0, and the age group is higher vulnerability of COVID than other age groups. Conversely, alternative \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
